rmatting applies to both counts and lamports; `\"0\"` stays bare.\n  - Zero-filled row: a fully-zero per-game row renders literal `\"0\"`\n    across all 8 numeric cells (preserves measured-zero semantics — FR-4\n    forbids em-dashes for measured zeros).\n  - Empty state: `rows={[]}` renders the operator status block pointing\n    at `game_entries`; no `<table>` element rendered.\n  - Error state: an `error` prop renders the alert and suppresses both\n    the table and the empty status.\n- Targeted check (peek): `pnpm test --run` ✅ (267/267, +17 from\n  iteration 31's 250), `pnpm lint` ✅, `pnpm typecheck` ✅.\nEOF\necho \"history appended\"","description":"Append iteration 32 history entry"},"caller":{"type":"direct"}}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":354,"cache_read_input_tokens":110995,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":354},"output_tokens":69,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"diagnostics":null,"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"d8601274-731d-45e4-bbc0-4bd6247d591a","uuid":"f576db19-9c1e-48e6-a124-7d17faa91c1d"}
